{\listtext	\'95	}4 small lemons, thinly sliced\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 (750 ml) bottles sparkling wine or {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/champagne/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Champagne}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 liter seltzer or sparkling water\
